OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782915513
OL,3,CViolent thug threw boiling water over
OL,4,Cpolice officer in Birmingham
OL,6,FThis was the moment a violent thug
OL,7,Fthrew boiling water over a police
OL,8,Fofficer as they tried to detain him.
OL,10,FTwo officers were called to a
OL,11,Fdisturbance in the garden of John
OL,12,FDavies' Birmingham home, where they
OL,13,Ffound he had another man cornered
OL,14,Fagainst a fence.
OL,16,FAfter one of the officers split the
OL,17,Fmen up, Davies went back in his house.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782915513
OL,3,CViolent thug threw boiling water over
OL,4,Cpolice officer in Birmingham
OL,6,FThe other man told the officers that
OL,7,FDavies had a knife. Davies was
OL,8,Fconfronted about the knife by the
OL,9,Fofficers, but he denied it.
OL,11,FDavies then threw a hot drink he had
OL,12,Fmade into the face of the man he'd
OL,13,Fbeen arguing with.
OL,15,FBody worn footage from the officers
OL,16,Fthen shows that when police tried to
OL,17,Farrest him, he punched one in the face.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782915513
OL,3,CViolent thug threw boiling water over
OL,4,Cpolice officer in Birmingham
OL,6,FHe then went on to grab a recently-
OL,7,Fboiled kettle and poured the water
OL,8,Fover another officer, leaving her with
OL,9,Fblistering over her shoulders, back
OL,10,Fand neck.
OL,12,FDavies was jailed for his actions.
OL,14,FDC Manpreet Sidhu, from the
OL,15,Fneighbourhood crime team at
OL,16,FBournville, said: "This was a
OL,17,Fhorrendous attack on two officers
OL,18,Fgoing about their duties.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782915513
OL,3,CViolent thug threw boiling water over
OL,4,Cpolice officer in Birmingham
OL,6,F"You can see from the footage that
OL,7,FDavies put up a struggle and it took
OL,8,Fmany officers to restrain him so that
OL,9,Fhe could be brought into custody.
OL,11,F"One of the officers involved suffered
OL,12,Fsignificant injuries and has only
OL,13,Frecently been able to return to work
OL,14,Ffollowing this assault.
OL,16,F"No one should have to face this level
OL,17,Fof violence simply for doing their job
OL,18,Fand I hope the sentence delivered to
OL,19,FDavies provides some justice for those
OL,20,Finvolved.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782915513
OL,3,CViolent thug threw boiling water over
OL,4,Cpolice officer in Birmingham
OL,6,F"This will have a lasting impact on
OL,7,Fthe officers but now Davies is where
OL,8,Fhe firmly belongs in prison."
OL,10,FDavies went on to admit maliciously
OL,11,Fwounding the PC he scalded with intent
OL,12,Fto resist arrest, assaulting the
OL,13,Fofficer he punched and assaulting the
OL,14,Fman he'd been arguing with when
OL,15,Fofficers arrived.
OL,17,FThe 58-year-old, of Talbot Street,
OL,18,FWinson Green, was jailed for 14 years
OL,19,Fand six months at Birmingham Crown
OL,20,FCourt on Friday.
OL,26,@pD@]O]
