OL,3,CViolent thug threw boiling water over
OL,4,Cpolice officer in Birmingham
OL,6,FHe was given an extended licence
OL,7,Fperiod of four years.
OL,9,FBoth officers have returned to work.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/6
